## âš™ï¸ Basic Setup

```bash
enable                          # Enter privileged EXEC mode
configure terminal              # Enter global configuration mode
hostname SWITCH_NAME            # Set hostname
no ip domain-lookup             # Disable DNS lookup (to avoid typos causing delays)
```

---

## ğŸ” Set Passwords

```bash
enable secret YOUR_PASSWORD     # Set encrypted enable password

line console 0
  password YOUR_PASSWORD        # Console access password
  login
exit

line vty 0 4
  password YOUR_PASSWORD        # Telnet/SSH access password
  login
exit
```

---

## ğŸŒ Interface Configuration

```bash
interface FastEthernet0/1
  description Connected to PC1
  switchport mode access
  switchport access vlan 10
  no shutdown
exit
```

---

## ğŸ“¦ VLAN Configuration

```bash
vlan 10
  name Sales
exit

interface range fa0/1 - 10
  switchport mode access
  switchport access vlan 10
exit
```

---

## ğŸ” Trunk Port Setup

```bash
interface fa0/24
  switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
  switchport mode trunk
  switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20
exit
```

---

## ğŸ’¾ Save Configuration

```bash
copy running-config startup-config
```

---

## ğŸ” Useful Show Commands

```bash
show vlan brief                 # Show all VLANs
show running-config            # Show current config
show mac address-table         # Display MAC address table
show interfaces status         # Show interface status and VLANs
show ip interface brief        # Quick IP/interface overview
```

